Convert text and images to Lycoris viewable format.

Supported formats
cover: png, jpeg, gif, bmp, tiff
files: txt, png, jpeg, gif, bmp, tiff

Input JSON example
{
  "title": "I Am a Cat",
  "cover": "cover.jpg",
  "files": [
    "chapter1.txt",
    "chapter2.txt",
    "chapter3.txt"
  ]
}

Command example
> node main.js -i ./input.json -o ./output

* Before executing this command, execute the following command.
> npm install

